                  title="Fully remote working">remotely</abbr> from Cape Town, South Africa.</p>
              <p class="content">My main skills and experience are in technical leadership, <abbr title="HTML5">HTML</abbr>, <abbr
                  title="SASS, SCSS">CSS</abbr>, <abbr
                  title="ECMAScript ES 5/6/2015, jQuery, or Stimulus">JavaScript</abbr>, <abbr
                  title="An open source object-relational database system">PostgreSQL</abbr>, and Ruby on Rails. I am
                also capable in <abbr title="Flask, Connexion">Python</abbr> and <abbr
                  title="Tensorflow and PyTorch">Machine
                  Learning</abbr>.</p>
              <p class="content">Currently I am the <abbr title="Chief Technical Officer">CTO</abbr> of <a
                  href="https://openup.org.za" rel="noopener">OpenUp</a>. I have worked with <a
                  href="https://caliberai.net" rel="noopener">CaliberAI</a> (CTO), <a
                  href="https://kinzen.com" rel="noopener">Kinzen</a> (CTO &amp; co-founder), <a
                  href="https://storyful.com" rel="noopener">Storyful</a> (CTO, acquired by News Corp), <a
                  href="https://www.redhat.com/en/about/press-releases/red-hat-acquire-feedhenry-adds-enterprise-mobile-application-platform"
                  rel="noopener">FeedHenry</a> (co-founder, acquired by Red Hat), and <a href="https://changex.org"
                  rel="noopener">ChangeX</a>.</p>
              <p class="content">Now that you know a bit about me, <a href="mailto:hello@paulmwatson.com"
                  title="Email hello@paulmwatson.com">say
                  hello</a>.</p>
            </div>
            <footer class="card-footer">
              <a class="card-footer-item" href="https://tilde.zone/@paulmwatson" rel="noopener" title="Mastodon">
                Mastodon
              </a>
              <a class="card-footer-item" href="https://github.com/paulmwatson" rel="noopener" title="GitHub">
                GitHub
              </a>
              <a class="card-footer-item" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/paulmwatson" rel="noopener"
